          "Limitations"
        ],
        [
          "Higher Education",
          "E-Learning",
          "Hybrid ",
          "Next Course to Take",
          "40 undergraduate students",
          "Computer Science Program",
          "Questionnaire,\nEnrollment History\n",
          "Learners are represented by the Quuestionnaire and Academic History.",
          "Requires retraining to change results.  ",
          "Learners are represented as personality (from questionnaire) and profile (from the remaning data). Both attributes are normalized and fed into a kNN algorithm (after normalization). Distance uses Hamming (sequences) and Cosine similarity (personality).",
          "Top-N Courses",
          "{Accuracy: 0.91 - PERKC}",
          "Authors look to do some form of Collaborative Filtering to compute similarity between users (without the need for rating). \n\nThe goal is to perform sequence prediction rather than perform Sequential Pattern Mining.",
          "- Small set of students in test\n\n- Only Accuracy is used to evaluate the results.\n\n- Learners are required to answer the questionnaire to be initialized.\n\n"
        ]
      ],
      "index": 5
    }
  ],
