    {
      "id": "1b44750c-f3ba-80d4-bef8-caf415f44cf8",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Students often select e-learning options to gain extra credits and and enhance their skills. The authors propose a personalizer recommender system that use Compact Prediction Tree to recommend courses for students to take. Algorithm is tested against other baseline approaches and is shown to outperform the alternatives. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1b44750c-f3ba-80d4-bef8-caf415f44cf8",
        "parent": {
